work.work-title: Lamb of God, whose dying love

credit.credit-words: By Thine agonizing pain, And bloody sweat, we pray, By Thy dying love to man, Take all our sins away; Burst our bonds, and set us free, From iniquity release; O remember Calvary, And bid us go in peace.
Lamb of God, whose dying love

direction-type.words: And bid us go in peace.
